				<p>Decatur Legacy is a membership organization made up of charitable organizations and professional advisors -accountants, attorneys, wealth managers, financial advisors - who encourage supporters, donors, volunteers, and clients to include a gift to charity in their wills or estate plans.</p>
				<p>Leaving a legacy to your community allows people from all walks of life to make a difference even after they are gone.</p>
				<p>To learn more about how you can leave a legacy to your favorite charity, contact any of the Decatur Legacy members, or call 217.429.3000.</p>
